    <h2
      class="mb-6 font-sans text-2xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-none tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:mx-auto"
    >
      Looking for the mailing list?
    </h2>

    <a
      href="https://groups.google.com/a/lbl.gov/g/warewulf"
      target="_blank"
      class="rounded-md bg-green-700 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-green-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-green-600"
      aria-label="Join Mailing List"
      title="Join Mailing List"
    >
      Join Mailing List
